:#  Filename:	    regx.bat						      #
:#                                                                            #
:#  Description:    Manage the registry "directories"=keys and "files"=values #
:#                                                                            #
:#  Notes:	    Front end to Windows' reg.exe.			      #
:#		    Uses the familiar dir, type, tree, set, del, rd commands  #
